sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Customer
    participant UI as Mobile/Web App
    participant BFF as Web/Mobile BFF
    participant Orch as Onboarding Orchestrator
    participant IDV as IDV Service (3rd Party)

    Note over Customer, IDV: Trigger Verification Step
    UI->>BFF: POST /onboarding/{sessionId}/verify
    BFF->>Orch: Route request
    Orch-->>UI: 202 Accepted (State: VERIFICATION_PENDING)
    
    par Async Processing & Polling
        loop UI Polling (Every 3-5s)
            UI->>BFF: GET /onboarding/{sessionId}/status
            BFF->>Orch: Route request
            Orch-->>UI: 200 OK (State: VERIFICATION_PENDING)
            Note over Customer, UI: UI shows: "We’re reviewing your information. This may take a few minutes."
        end
    and Backend IDV Integration
        Orch->>IDV: POST /verify (Trigger OCR, face match)
        
        Note right of IDV: 3rd-party provider experiences latency/timeout or enforces strict rate limits
        IDV-->>Orch: 504 Gateway Timeout or 429 Too Many Requests
        
        Note over Orch: System applies Retry/Backoff pattern
        
        Orch->>IDV: POST /verify (Retry attempt 1 after delay)
        IDV-->>Orch: 200 OK (Verified)
        
        Note over Orch: State transitions to ACCOUNT_CREATION_PENDING
    end

    UI->>BFF: GET /onboarding/{sessionId}/status
    BFF->>Orch: Route request
    Orch-->>UI: 200 OK (State: ACCOUNT_CREATION_PENDING)
    Note over Customer, UI: Customer journey proceeds smoothly despite backend timeout